headline: Ortega Reimagines Taco Night with Cheez-It™ Flavored Taco Shells
summary: Ortega, a leading brand of Mexican food products including taco shells, taco kits, Mexican seasonings, peppers and the number-one-selling brand of taco sauce in the United States, announced today the launch of Cheez-It™ Flavored Taco Shells - a revolutionary taco shell that fuses the cheesy burst of flavor of Cheez-It™ crackers that you crave with the iconic crunch of the Ortega Hard Taco Shell. A snackable shell that's as flavorful as the fillings inside, the Ortega Cheez-It™ Flavored Taco Shel
